    "rank": 1,
    "text": "Your apparition casts a feral shadow over your form. You can polymorph into any form listed in *pest form*. When you transform into a form granted by a spell, you gain all the effects of the form you chose from a version of the spell heightened to darkened forest form's rank. Each time you Sustain this Spell, you can choose to change to a different shape from those available via any of the associated spells.",
